title: Brooklyn Nets, Trae Young, Harden Watch | WHAT’S BURNIN’ | Ep 1
itunes:title: Brooklyn Nets, Trae Young, Harden Watch | WHAT’S BURNIN’ | Ep 1
description:
On this weeks edition of WHAT’S BURNIN’, Matt and Stak breakdown the opening week of NBA play. The boys discuss the Nets hot start and the state of the team after losing Spencer Dinwiddie. Plus, they discuss the solid start from a bunch of young teams across the NBA, including Trae Young and the Hawks. Also, the James Harden watch continues.
